item.title: About
item.description: Sophia Roessler is a 17 year old photographer who attends Woodinville High School as a Senior. She shoots a diverse range of subjects and styles, all to better suit the subject. Are you looking for a professional headshot for a LinkedIn profile? Are you a graduating senior who needs a portrait? Or perhaps you are an artist/musician/athlete who needs their talents showcased in a photo portfolio? Sophia Roessler is a skilled 17 year old photographer
